["58114"]={["Title"]="", 
    ["1"]="\"<HTML>$B<body>$B<h1>Group of Homeless Samaritans Brutally Murdered Behind Furlbrow Farm $B</h1>$B<BR/>$B<p>$BWitnesses state that the four men killed at the Furlbrow\'s farm were on their way to delivering dirt pies to a shelter on the east coast when attacked. $BJimb \\\"\"Candles\\\"\" McHannigan, an eyewitness on the scene, had this to say, \\\"\"Yep, I saw the whole thing go down with my own two eyes. Was a male hunter. He looked like he may have been on something. He slaughtered the poor bums in broad daylight while shouting obscenities and proclaiming his love for Stormwind and King Varian Wrynn. I think he may have killed Lou immediately afterward. I was too shaken up to see.\\\"\"$B</p>$B</body>$B</HTML>$B$B$B$B$B\"", }, 
